78
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:10,879
Thank you, President Lu.

79
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:20,859
Two.

80
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:27,319
Slide your arm.

81
00:05:27,319 --> 00:05:29,119
Sister Jiao.

82
00:05:29,119 --> 00:05:31,739
