251
00:17:04,059 --> 00:17:06,239
Yes, that's fair enough.

252
00:17:06,239 --> 00:17:08,119
How about this, Jian'an?

253
00:17:08,119 --> 00:17:09,618
Leave it to me.

254
00:17:09,618 --> 00:17:12,319
