258
00:17:21,859 --> 00:17:24,720
Okay, it's up to you.

259
00:17:25,580 --> 00:17:27,500
Go get some rest.

260
00:17:28,280 --> 00:17:30,319
- I am going to take a bath now.
- Okay.

